title: Trump Calls Justice, FBI ‘Missing in Action’ on Election Allegations
sub_head: Federal officials and state election authorities agree they have seen no evidence of tampering with voting systems
body:
WASHINGTON—President Trump accused federal law-enforcement agencies run by his own appointees of ignoring his claims of mass election fraud, as his legal setbacks continued to mount.
“Missing in action,” Mr. Trump said during an interview Sunday on Fox News. “You would think if you’re in the FBI or Department of Justice, this is the biggest thing you could be looking at. Where are they? I’ve not seen anything.”
